Start
    Input number of frames
    Input reference string
    Initialize empty list for frames
    page_faults = 0
    For each page in reference string:
        If page in frame:
            Move page to most recent position
        Else:
            If frames not full:
                Add page
            Else:
                Remove least recently used page
                Add new page
            Increment page_faults
    Display total page faults
Stop
